  "bio_raw": "From 2014- August 2018: Aminuzzaman has 4 years’ experience in teaching in the Department of Film, Television and Digital Media at the Green University of Bangladesh. He also has 10 years’ experience in professional photography and teaching as a part-time faculty at Pathshala, The South Asian Media Institute in Dhaka. He was involved in the production of international documentaries for BBC Earth Report as a researcher, camera and sound person in Bangladesh and India. He Worked in Drik India, Kolkata, India as a photographer from Aug 2004-July 2005.",
